OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with outbreaks of rain,
OL,8,Fwhich may be heavy at times. Winds
OL,9,Fstrong at times, especially near the
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA mixed day of bright or sunny
OL,13,Fspells and showers, which may be heavy
OL,14,Fat times. Strong southwesterly winds
OL,15,Fwhich may reach gale force before
OL,16,Feasing in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
