OL,6,Fspells and showers on Monday. Dry
OL,7,Fstart with rain later on Tuesday.
OL,8,FMostly cloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,9,Fon Wednesday. Winds light Monday then
OL,10,Fbreezy on Tuesday and Wednesday.
